
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-wing-dhc-dns-reconfigure-02.txt'>
    <title>"DHCPv6 Dynamic Reconfiguration", Prashanth Patil, Mohamed Boucadair, Dan Wing, Tirumaleswar Reddy</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-wing-dhc-dns-reconfigure-02.txt</link>
    <description>This specification extends DHCPv6 so that a DHCPv6 Relay Agent can dynamically indicate end host connectivity to a DHCPv6 Server.  This information is also triggered by any change in connectivity type provided to the host.  The DHCPv6 server uses this information as an input to its decision-making about configuration parameters to be conveyed to that host.</description>
    <dc:date>2013-09-12T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
